Package com.syncura360.controller

Class ServicesController

java.lang.Object
com.syncura360.controller.ServicesController
@RestController @CrossOrigin(origins="*") @RequestMapping("/services") public class ServicesController extends Object
Controller responsible for handling services-related operations such as creating, updating, deleting, and retrieving services in a hospital. It supports CRUD operations on services and their associated attributes. The operations are protected by authentication and authorization mechanisms.
Author:
Benjamin Leiby
